			<div class="content">It is a nice feature to have for certain.<br />i looked at the Artemis java Code and the implementation if pretty simple, i was thinking about using some C# features to make the Aspects even cooler.<br />Maybe letting the user specify some custom delegate and provide it own customized filter could be nice.<br /><br />I also sow that the Java implementation is using Annotations for Mappers, this is also a cool stuff to have (maybe expand it idea and use annotation in more places like the Systems)</div>

			

